Class EmptyDocument

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.guardtime.envelope.document.EmptyDocument
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Document, EnvelopeElement, AutoCloseable

    public class EmptyDocument
extends Object
    Represents a document in a envelope which doesn't store the document data in the same envelope (detached document).
